1. To support url encoding with utf-8

In standalone.xml (.config/config/)

Add 
    <system-properties>
        <!-- URI Properties -->
        <property name="org.apache.catalina.connector.URI_ENCODING" value="UTF-8"/>
        <property name="org.apache.catalina.connector.USE_BODY_ENCODING_FOR_QUERY_STRING" value="true"/>
    </system-properties>
    
After 
<extensions>
.
.
.
</extensions>


2. Grails workaround
Add In hibernate {}
    validator.apply_to_ddl = false
    validator.autoregister_listeners = false
    
3. Remove 
dataSource {
    pooled = true
    driverClassName = "org.h2.Driver"
    username = "sa"
    password = ""
}

4. Create jboss-classloading.xml && jboss-scanning.xml
    or use jboss plugin (generate-jboss-deploy 6 [for as 6 and 7])
    

